::DarkMouse::

She looked up as the other bot walked in.  She jumped to her feet and 
crouched away from both of them in the corner.  She trembled as the 
threat of her life ending was still very real.  She kept her eyes on 
both bots, hoping to see a chance to run, but still didn't see any.  
She sniffled and wiped her face with her hand.  She ws filled with 
terror as she silently prayed to the matrix that she get out of this 
alive.  But then, she still had one small ace up her sleeve, her own 
mech fluid.
